reviewText: This DVD has a lot of fills that can easily be applied to what ever your style. The PDF file is case sensitive when typing in the URL if that is any help. Randy has an approachable personality and throw in a little humor you will not be disappointed.

I had to add this after seeing the comment above the PDF file is downloadable and the site is on the dvd cover. The dvd is filled with lots of content and little to no B.S. Randy is a great instructor no boring junk just lots of useful information.
